{"tid":1691682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 突破！發夢見三個情景","createTime":"2019-11-03T18:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T19:18:28.000Z","uid":244058,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"35fcd069ec4598cf9b2ebbf734a9140a2ab554b6","tid":1691682,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:14:08.000Z","msg":"訓覺發夢醒左 一共發左三個夢...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有個男仔問我<br />\n「可否發起罷工一星期<br />\n要大家去超市街市買野儲糧個種<br />\n有打仗逃亡個種緊張感<br />\n先會令大家醒覺」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個夢見到<br />\n「司機集體棄車塞路<br />\n樓上民居一齊發起攻擊<br />\n火燒狗屋<br />\n有人吹號角用聲音指引」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後一個夢<br />\n「有巨人發起魔法師活動日<br />\n貼埋說明書<br />\n令和理非都可以輕鬆加入<br />\n使用魔法全城焦土」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以整理下<br />\n成為遊戲新任務"},{"pid":"46daff6740b1d20a43b770d5f37ae05e77838474","tid":1691682,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:17:52.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[日常文宣] [文宣方向] 以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"211fa2596fff378db294ec5d7944bc043e42c78a","tid":1691682,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:19:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人瞓醒繼續起身返工？<br />\n捨得長期三罷未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"72f06f349ed4171d983c8cc826583c77ea7210e9","tid":1691682,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6d83f7eb19700d2cf4ce0448ec00398be39738","tid":1691682,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"211fa2596fff378db294ec5d7944bc043e42c78a","tid":1691682,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply